Package: svAssert
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Title: 'SciViews::R' - Assertions and Meaningful Error Messages
Description: Assertions combining `is_xxx()` and `stop_xxx()` functions for
  maximum flexibility. Enhanced error messages for 'SciViews::R' based on
  `cli::cli_abort()` and `rlang::abort()` but also allowing message translation,
  including for messages in other package, or after the error is thrown.
